<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Kan Pathian a ttha, Kan Pathian a ttha
 Amah nak in ttha, an um lo,
 Bawi vialte lak ah, Bawi bik Cungnung bik
 Kan Pathian a ttha, Halleluijah.

[C1]
   Halleluijah, aw Halleluijah
   Ka nunnak Bawipa thangthat tuah
   Ka sualnak a ka ngaihthiam, Ka zawtnak a ka damter
   Kan Pathian a ttha, Halleluijah.

[V2]
 Kan Pathian a tthawng, Kan Pathian a tthawng
 Amah nak i tthawng, an um lo,
 Bawi vialte lak ah, Bawi bik Cungnung bik
 Kan Pathian a tthawng, Halleluijah.

[V3]
 Kan Pathian a lian, Kan Pathian a lian
 Amah nak i lian, an um lo,
 Bawi vialte lak ah, Bawi bik Cungnung bik
 kan Pathian a lian, Halleluijah.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>KAN PATHIAN A TTHA</title>
</song>